<p>In this image <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Li8rd.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Li8rd.png" alt="enter image description here"></a> How can I use <code>touchDragged</code> to drag this <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/3mrCx.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/3mrCx.png" alt="enter image description here"></a> in <code>x</code> axis only ??</p>  <p>This is my code to make this action:</p>  <pre><code>iBtnDrag = new Image(tBtnDrag); iBtnDrag.addListener(new ClickListener() {          @Override         public boolean touchDown(InputEvent event, float x, float y, int pointer, int button) {             return true;         }          @Override         public void touchDragged(InputEvent event, float x, float y, int pointer) {             iBtnDrag.setPosition(x, 448, Align.center);         } }); </code></pre>